21448/http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1960s.html |archive-date=22 November 2005 |accessdate=7 July 2016}}</ref>||{{dts|format=dmy|1966|July|30}} || BBC1/ITV\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|2 || [[Funeral of Diana, Princess of Wales]] || 32.10<ref name=\"BFI-1990s\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1990s.html |title=Features &#124; Britain's Most Watched TV &#124; 1990s |publisher=British Film Institute (BFI) |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051125215025/http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1990s.html |archivedate=25 November 2005 |accessdate=7 July 2016}}</ref> ||{{dts|format=dmy|1997|September|6}} || BBC1/ITV\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|3 || [[Royal Family (documentary)|''Royal Family'' (documentary)]] || 30.69<ref name=\"BFI-1960s\" /> ||{{dts|format=dmy|1969|June|21}} and {{dts|format=dmy|1969|June|28}} || BBC1/ITV\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|4 || [[Apollo 13]] [[Splashdown (spacecraft landing)|splashdown]] || 28.60<ref name=\"BFI-1970s\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1970s.html |title=Features &#124; Britain's Most Watched TV &#124; 1970s |publisher=British Film Institute (BFI) |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051122221511/http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1970s.html |archive-date=22 November 2005 |accessdate=7 July 2016}}</ref> ||{{dts|format=dmy|1970|April|17}} || BBC1/ITV\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|5 || [[1970 FA Cup Final|1970 FA Cup Final replay]] || 28.49<ref name=\"BFI-1970s\" /> ||{{dts|format=dmy|1970|April|29}} || BBC1/ITV\n|-\n| align=\"center\"|6 || [[Wedding of Charles, Prince of Wales, and Lady Diana Spencer]] || 28.40<ref name=\"BFI-1980s\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1980s.html |title=Features &#124; Britain's Most Watched TV &#124; 1980s |publisher=British Film Institute (BFI) |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051122221538/http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/mostwatched/1980s.html |archive-date= 22 November 2005 |accessdate=7 July