a website that provides a [[Web directory|directory]] of [[torrent file]]s and [[Magnet URI scheme|magnet links]] used for [[peer-to-peer file sharing]] through the [[BitTorrent]] protocol.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/torrent-site-1337x-hopes-new-design-will-prevent-search-engine-bans-161030/|title=Torrent Site 1337x Hopes New Design Will Prevent Search Engine Bans - TorrentFreak|date=2016-10-30|newspaper=TorrentFreak|language=en-US|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> According to the [[TorrentFreak]] news blog, 1337x is the third most popular torrent website as of 2018.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/top-10-most-popular-torrent-sites-of-2018-180107/|title=Top 10 Most Popular Torrent Sites of 2018 - TorrentFreak|date=2018-01-07|work=TorrentFreak|access-date=2018-06-23|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\n1337x was founded in 2007 and saw increasing popularity in 2016 after the closure of [[KickassTorrents]].<ref name=\":0\" /> In October 2016, it introduced a website redesign with new functionalities.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.techtimes.com/articles/184320/20161031/1337x-takes-on-the-pirate-bay-as-torrentz-and-kickass-torrents-alternative-unveils-new-site-design.htm|title=1337x Takes On The Pirate Bay As Torrentz And Kickass Torrents Alternative Unveils New Site Design|last=Times|first=Tech|date=2016-10-31|newspaper=Tech Times|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> The site is banned from [[Google]] search queries and does not appear when searching through [[Google Search|Google search]].<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\" /> This action was taken following request by Feelgood Entertainment in 2015.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lumendatabase.org/notices/1623131|title=DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google :: Notices :: Lumen|website=www.lumendatabase.org|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> In 2015 the site moved from its older [[.pl]] domain to [[.to]], partly in order to evade the block.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/1337x-staff-abandon-insecure-torrent-site-start-over-151220/|title=1337x Staff Abandon \"Insecure\" Torrent Site, Start Over - TorrentFreak|date=2015-12-20|newspaper=TorrentFreak|language=en-US|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref>\n\nIt has been touted as an alternative to [[The Pirate Bay]] in face of its potential demise.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gamenguide.com/articles/56304/20161018/kickass-torrent-crisis-news-update-pirate-bay-kills-all-competitions-kickasstorrents-kat-torrentz-torrent-hound-no-more.htm|title=Kickass Torrent Crisis News & Update: Pirate Bay Kills All Competitions; KickassTorrents (KAT), Torrentz, Torrent Hound No More?|last=Guide|first=Game &|date=2016-10-18|newspaper=Gamenguide|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.universityherald.com/articles/45724/20161024/the-pirate-bay-alternatives-tpb-extra-torrent-yts-1337x-google-chrome-browser-mozilla-firefox.htm |title=The Pirate Bay Alternative: Google Hits TPB With A New Block [VIDEO]; See Top Three Alternatives |last=Patel |first=Vinay |date=24 October 2016 |website=www.universityherald.com |archive-url=https://archive.is/20161025045047/http://www.universityherald.com/articles/45724/20161024/the-pirate-bay-alternatives-tpb-extra-torrent-yts-1337x-google-chrome-browser-mozilla-firefox.htm |archive-date=25 October 2016 |access-date=2016-10-31 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.latinpost.com/articles/125482/20161026/pirate-bay-site.htm|title=The Pirate Bay has shut down, but users can try these alternatives|last=Post|first=Latin|date=2016-10-26|newspaper=Latin Post|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n*[[Comparison of BitTorrent sites]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{official website|https://1337x.to/}}\n\n{{filesharing}}\n{{Bittorrent}}\n\n[[Category:BitTorrent]]\n[[Category:BitTorrent websites]]\n[[Category:Web directories]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|BitTorrent-related website}}\n\n{{Infobox website\n| name             = 1337x\n| logo             = 1337X logo.svg\n| logo_size        = 160px\n| logo_caption     = <!-- or:\n| logocaption      =  -->\n| logo_alt         = \n| screenshot       = 1337x Homepage July 2019.png\n| area_served      = Worldwide\n| screenshot_size  = \n| caption          = 1337x Homepage as of July 2019\n| screenshot_alt   = \n| collapsible      = <!-- set as \"on\", \"y\", etc, otherwise omit/leave blank -->\n| collapsetext     = <!-- collapsible area's heading (default \"Screenshot\"); omit/leave blank if collapsible not set -->\n| url              = [https://1337x.to 1337x.to]\n| commercial       = <!-- \"Yes\", \"No\" or leave blank -->\n| type             = Torrent index, [[Magnet URI scheme|magnet links]] provider\n| registration     = Optional, free\n| language         = \n| num_users        = \n| content_license  = <!-- or:\n| content_licence  = -->\n| owner            = <!-- or:\n| owners           = -->\n| author           = <!-- or: creator / authors / creators -->\n| editor           = <!-- or:\n| editors          = -->\n| revenue          = \n| alexa            = {{decrease}} 258 ({{as of|2019|July|alt=July 2019}})<ref name=\"alexa\">{{cite web |url= http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/1337x.to |title=1337x.to Site Info |work=[[Alexa Internet|Alexa]] |accessdate=16 July 2019}}</ref>\n| issn             = <!-- ISSN, e.g. 1085-6706 (automatically linked to http://www.WorldCat.org) -->\n| oclc             = <!-- OCLC number, useful where an ISSN has not been allocated (automatically linked to http://www.WorldCat.org) -->\n| launch_date      = {{Start date and age|df=yes|2007}}\n| current_status   = Online\n| footnotes        = \n| background       = <!-- for collapsetext heading; default grey (gainsboro) -->\n| programming_language= [[HTML]], [[JavaScript]], and [[PHP]]\n}}{{filesharing sidebar}}\n\n'''1337x''' is a website that provides a [[Web directory|directory]] of [[torrent file]]s and [[Magnet URI scheme|magnet links]] used for [[peer-to-peer file sharing]] through the [[BitTorrent]] protocol.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/torrent-site-1337x-hopes-new-design-will-prevent-search-engine-bans-161030/|title=Torrent Site 1337x Hopes New Design Will Prevent Search Engine Bans - TorrentFreak|date=2016-10-30|newspaper=TorrentFreak|language=en-US|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> According to the [[TorrentFreak]] news blog, 1337x is the third most popular torrent website as of 2018.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/top-10-most-popular-torrent-sites-of-2018-180107/|title=Top 10 Most Popular Torrent Sites of 2018 - TorrentFreak|date=2018-01-07|work=TorrentFreak|access-date=2018-06-23|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\n1337x was founded in 2007 and saw increasing popularity in 2016 after the closure of [[KickassTorrents]].<ref name=\":0\" /> In October 2016, it introduced a website redesign with new functionalities.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.techtimes.com/articles/184320/20161031/1337x-takes-on-the-pirate-bay-as-torrentz-and-kickass-torrents-alternative-unveils-new-site-design.htm|title=1337x Takes On The Pirate Bay As Torrentz And Kickass Torrents Alternative Unveils New Site Design|last=Times|first=Tech|date=2016-10-31|newspaper=Tech Times|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> The site is banned from [[Google]] search queries and does not appear when searching through [[Google Search|Google search]].<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\" /> This action was taken following request by Feelgood Entertainment in 2015.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lumendatabase.org/notices/1623131|title=DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google :: Notices :: Lumen|website=www.lumendatabase.org|access-date=2016-10-31}}</ref> In 2015 the site moved from its older [[.pl]] domain to [[.to]], partly in order to evade the block.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref na